@page "/docs/toolbar"

<PageTitle>Toolbar - Tldraw.Blazor Docs</PageTitle>

<div class="docs-content">
    <h1>Toolbar</h1>
    <p class="docs-lead">The top toolbar provides tool selection, export/import, zoom controls, and utility buttons.</p>

    <h2 id="tools">
        Tool Buttons
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#tools">#</a>
    </h2>
    <p>12 tool buttons with active state highlighting:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>▢ Select, ✋ Hand, ✏️ Draw</li>
        <li>▭ Rect, ⬭ Ellipse, ◇ Diamond, ⭐ Star, ⬡ Hex, △ Tri</li>
        <li>𝐓 Text, ➜ Arrow, 🧹 Erase</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="export">
        Export/Import
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#export">#</a>
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li>💾 JSON — export to clipboard</li>
        <li>🖼️ PNG — download as file</li>
        <li>📂 Import — load from clipboard</li>
        <li>🖼️+ Image — add image from file picker</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="zoom">
        Zoom Controls
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#zoom">#</a>
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li>➖/➕ — zoom out/in</li>
        <li>⊞ Fit — reset to fit all shapes</li>
        <li>1:1 — reset to 100% zoom</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 id="utility">
        Utility
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#utility">#</a>
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li>⌨️ — toggle keyboard shortcuts help</li>
        <li>🌙 — toggle dark mode</li>
    </ul>
</div>
